    <h2 align="center">Zach Parker</h2>

    <table align="center" width="60%" style="background: #f5f5dc;border-radius:1em;padding:1em">
      <tr>
        <td>
          <p>
            Welcome to my site!  This site tracks my progress and the goals I have for my hobbies.  By day, I'm a math/data/programming person.  I have a PhD in economics.  But this site isn't about any of that.
          </p>
          <ul>
            <li> I've been working on a fantasy novel based on a world I started thinking about during the pandemic.  I wrote part of a role-playing game in the world, then about 50-60 thousands words of an all-over the place draft + wiki of world building stuff, then I wrote an outline, and now I'm sitting down to really write the story. Current progress: about 100,000 words in which I'd guesstimate is about 60 percent done for the first draft.  
            <li> Playing Chess &mdash; <s>Current goal is to get to 1900 on Chess.com Rapid.</s> I made it!  Next: 2000!
          </ul>
        </td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td>
          <p>
            Below are links to where you can find me on the internet:
